   http://banshee-project.org/files/ipod-sharp/ipod-sharp-0.6.3.tar.gz

 * libipoddevice 0.5.3 Tarball:
   http://banshee-project.org/files/libipoddevice/libipoddevice-0.5.3.tar.gz

